content: Are we calling registered voters?  I have a person who thinks they were auto removed after a conviction in 2009, I gave him the website and call number to check, but I don't want to get people's hopes up if they are ineligible...
Yes we are calling voters. You did the right thing by sharing the hotline & website. That is the best we can do!
It's not always going to be perfect but we do what we can!
